##  NumPy Operations

### Arithmetic Operations
```python
a = np.array([1, 2, 3])
b = np.array([4, 5, 6])

print(a + b)    # [5 7 9]
print(a - b)    # [-3 -3 -3]
print(a * b)    # [4 10 18]
print(a / b)    # [0.25 0.4 0.5]
print(a ** 2)   # [1 4 9]
```

### Statistical Operations
```python
arr = np.array([10, 20, 30, 40, 50])

print(np.mean(arr))    # 30.0
print(np.median(arr))  # 30.0
print(np.std(arr))     # 14.14
print(np.min(arr))     # 10
print(np.max(arr))     # 50
print(np.sum(arr))     # 150
```
### ✅ Statistical Operations
```python
arr = np.array([10, 20, 30, 40, 50])

